member.summary:
For performance, it is better to unassign this material of the Entities before destroying it.
EX: renderer.material = null;
EX: Material.Remove(material);

For performance, it is better to unassign this material of the Entities before destroying it.
EX: rigidBody.material = null;
EX: PhysicMaterial.Remove(material);

For performance, it is better to unassign this renderTexture of the Entities before destroying it.
EX: renderTextureRenderer.renderTexture = null;
EX: RenderTexture.Remove(renderTexture);
